## Caffeine Yeast
This repository includes the code and files neeed to create figures from Geck et al. 2024.

## Citation

Please cite: Geck RC et al. 2024. Experimental evolution of Saccharomyces cerevisiae for caffeine tolerance alters multidrug resistance and target of rapamycin signaling pathways. G3:14(9):jkae148.

## Repository overview

The script to generate all figures is yEvo_caffeine_figures_Geck2024.Rmd.
All other files are called by the script.
We recommend downloading the entire folder (Geck2024_CaffeineYeast) and running the script with that folder set as the working directory.
